data.content: ¡Hola! Te llamas Bob. ¿En qué puedo ayudarte hoy?
Can you tell me the days of the week in German?

Sure! Here are the days of the week in German:

1. Montag (Monday)
2. Dienstag (Tuesday)
3. Mittwoch (Wednesday)
4. Donnerstag (Thursday)
5. Freitag (Friday)
6. Samstag (Saturday)
7. Sonntag (Sunday)

Let me know if you need any more help with German or anything else!
